--[[
AUTO RAID v53 - Maximum theoretical speed

Optimizations:
1. ChildAdded instant burst: kill breakables the FRAME they spawn
   (doesn't wait for scan loop - fires directly from event)
2. Smart burst: starts at 5, auto-increases if breakables survive 1st hit
   Lower burst = less lag = faster server response = faster room clears
3. Parallel chest+creation: fire chests AND start Leave simultaneously
   Chests process while we're leaving (saves ~1.5s per cycle)
4. Cached UIDs: zero workspace scanning during tap loop

Theory: 10 rooms × 200ms + 2s transition = ~4s minimum
Target: 8-12s realistic
]]

